---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Medical Care and Rehabilitation"
  description="Learn about the comprehensive medical care and rehabilitation services available to UK veterans through the Armed Forces Compensation Scheme, including long-term care, specialist treatments, and mental health support.">
  <div class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 mb-4">Medical Care and Rehabilitation</h1>
    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <p class="lead">The Armed Forces Compensation Scheme (AFCS) is committed to providing comprehensive medical care and rehabilitation services to veterans. Our goal is to support your recovery, manage ongoing conditions, and improve your quality of life.</p>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Long-term Care</h2>
        <p>For veterans requiring ongoing medical support, we offer:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access to specialised care facilities</li>
          <li>Home care services for those with severe disabilities</li>
          <li>Regular health assessments and care plan reviews</li>
          <li>Support for carers and family members</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Rehabilitation Services</h2>
        <p>Our rehabilitation programmes are designed to help you regain independence and improve your physical capabilities:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Physiotherapy and occupational therapy</li>
          <li>Prosthetics and orthotics services</li>
          <li>Adaptive sports and physical activity programmes</li>
          <li>Vocational rehabilitation to support return to work</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Specialist Treatments</h2>
        <p>We provide access to a range of specialist treatments for service-related conditions:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Advanced pain management techniques</li>
          <li>Neurological rehabilitation for brain and spinal injuries</li>
          <li>Audiology services for hearing-related issues</li>
          <li>Ophthalmic care for vision-related conditions</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Mental Health Care</h2>
        <p>Recognising the importance of mental health, we offer comprehensive support including:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Trauma-focused therapies for PTSD</li>
          <li>Cognitive Behavioural Therapy (CBT) for anxiety and depression</li>
          <li>Substance abuse treatment programmes</li>
          <li>Family therapy and relationship counselling</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>For more detailed information on each aspect of medical care and rehabilitation, please visit the specific pages linked in the sidebar.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="card bg-light mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Quick Links</h3>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li><a href="/medical/long-term-care" class="text-decoration-none">Long-term Care</a></li>
              <li><a href="/medical/rehabilitation" class="text-decoration-none">Rehabilitation Services</a></li>
              <li><a href="/medical/specialist-treatments" class="text-decoration-none">Specialist Treatments</a></li>
              <li><a href="/medical/mental-health" class="text-decoration-none">Mental Health Care</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Medical Support Helpline</h3>
            <p>For urgent medical advice or to discuss your care needs, contact our 24/7 helpline.</p>
            <p class="fw-bold">0800 XXX XXXX</p>
            <a href="/medical-support" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
